OpenSim::MuscleViaPoint

MuscleViaPoint Class Reference

#include <MuscleViaPoint.h>

Inheritance diagram for MuscleViaPoint:

List of all members.

Detailed Description

A class implementing a SIMM muscle via point, which is a muscle point that is active only for a specified range of a coordinate.

Author:
Peter Loan
Version:
1.0
